This map is obviously a de map, which is where the terrorists plant a bomb and the counter-terrorists defuse it. I feel that it is completed but if there is anything that anyone would like to suggest I would be happy to listen. 

I've checked many times for any errors or glitches and so far I haven't seemed to of found any. The bot navigation mesh works fine for me, and they do hide behind the crates.

Thanks a lot for viewing and please leave a comment or rating, thanks :)
